item.title: [HIVE-19992] Vectorization: Follow-on to HIVE-19951 --> add call to SchemaEvolution.isOnlyImplicitConversion to disable encoded LLAP I/O for ORC only when data type conversion is not implicit
item.description: When ORC-380 that adds the SchemaEvolution.isOnlyImplicitConversion call is available in the ORC release used by Apache master (and branch-3), then update LlapRecordReader (see comments in HIVE-19951 change).
item.summary: Vectorization: Follow-on to HIVE-19951 --> add call to SchemaEvolution.isOnlyImplicitConversion to disable encoded LLAP I/O for ORC only when data type conversion is not implicit

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
